All Implemented Interfaces:
android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2
public class DataGatheringService
extends android.app.Service

Service which controls starting and stopping of gathering data. It currently only controls the syncing of external data---received via Bluetooth---to the server but the gathering of device context data (such as location data) could also be controlled from here.
